VI Server Properties and Methods Not Supported in Real-Time Operating Systems

LabVIEW returns an error or unexpected results when it executes a call in a real-time operating system to a property or method in any of the following classes:

  • BuildSpecification Methods
  • BuildSpecification Properties
  • DataValRefNumConstant Methods
  • DataValRefNumConstant Properties
  • ExpressionNode Methods
  • ExpressionNode Properties
  • LibraryData Methods
  • LibraryData Properties
  • LVClassLibrary Methods
  • LVClassLibrary Properties
  • PropertyFolder Methods
  • PropertyFolder Properties
  • SharedVariableNode Methods
  • SharedVariableNode Properties
  • StatechartLibrary Methods
  • StatechartLibrary Properties
  • TextBaseNode Methods
  • TextBaseNode Properties
  • TypedRefNumConstant Methods
  • TypedRefNumConstant Properties
  • Variable Methods
  • Variable Properties
  • XControlLibrary Methods
  • XControlLibrary Properties
  • XInterfaceLibrary Methods
  • XInterfaceLibrary Properties
  • XNodeLibrary Methods
  • XNodeLibrary Properties
  • XPropertyFolder Methods
  • XPropertyFolder Properties
